CCPPPPTTAAIILL -- Environmental Variable

Append options to end of cpp command line
eexxppoorrtt CCPPPPTTAAIILL=_o_p_t_i_o_n_s

The COHERENT  C preprocessor ccpppp reads  the environmental variables CCPPPPHHEEAADD
and CCPPPPTTAAIILL before it begins its work.  You can set these variables to hold
the default options that you want the preprocessor always to use.

ccpppp appends the options in CCPPPPTTAAIILL to the end of its command line.

